                "title": "淬煉之劍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>。每回合第三次使用本技能時，傷害+2。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/d0e27bc7054292e95c673e6f491ff677_4053958865659999505.png",
                "id": "talent51596",
